## 🔍 SCHEMA MARKUP REQUIREMENTS

### **Product Schema (Required)**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Product",
  "name": "Product Name",
  "description": "400-word description",
  "image": ["image-url"],
  "sku": "product-id",
  "brand": {
    "@type": "Brand",
    "name": "Brand Name"
  },
  "offers": {
    "@type": "Offer",
    "url": "product-page-url",
    "priceCurrency": "USD",
    "price": "5.99",
    "priceValidUntil": "2025-12-31",
    "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock",
    "seller": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Amazon"
    }
  },
  "aggregateRating": {
    "@type": "AggregateRating",
    "ratingValue": "4.8",
    "reviewCount": "150"
  }
}
```

### **Breadcrumb Schema (Required)**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [...]
}
```

### **Additional Schemas to Consider:**
- FAQ schema (if FAQs present)
- Organization schema
- WebPage schema

