## 📊 SEO OPTIMIZATION REQUIREMENTS

### **On-Page SEO:**
- Unique H1 for each product (product name)
- 400-word unique description with semantic keywords
- Proper heading hierarchy (H1 → H2 → H3)
- Alt text for all images
- Internal links (10-15 per page minimum)
- Structured data (Product, Breadcrumb, FAQ schemas)
- Fast loading times (image optimization)
- Mobile-responsive design

### **Content Requirements:**
- No duplicate content across products
- Natural keyword integration (avoid keyword stuffing)
- Semantic keywords from provided lists
- Engaging, conversion-focused copy
- Clear product benefits
- Trust signals throughout

### **Technical SEO:**
- Canonical URLs
- Proper meta tags (title, description, OG tags)
- robots.txt friendly
- XML sitemap inclusion
- Fast Core Web Vitals
- Mobile-first design

